g.text: Herein, the vulnerability of bridges with clogged joints that are sub-
jected to temperature rise is quantified in terms of the interaction equation. A total of 89,089
simply supported steel girder bridges (SSSG) with compact section are evaluated. In this study
we chose to evaluate only compact sections since the section capacity is governed by plastic
behavior. The capacity of non-compact sections could have also been evaluated but would
require much more information than what was readily available in the NBI database.
